      "content": "i know there are people to call, but it doesn't change the fact that the world just keeps moving while i'm stuck in this void. it feels so heavy. sometimes i look at the empty side of the bed and i just think... why am i still here? why am i fighting so hard to stay in a world that doesn't have him in it anymore?",
